  <brief_title>Remifentanil And Local Anesthesia Compared With Local Anesthesia For The Insertion Of Central Venous Catheters</brief_title>
  <acronym>REMIDOLCATH</acronym>
  <official_title>REMIFENTANIL AND LOCAL ANESTHESIA COMPARED WITH LOCAL ANESTHESIA FOR THE INSERTION OF CENTRAL VENOUS CATHETERS IN AWAKE PATIENTS</official_title>
